OL,3,CSean Brown family to challenge
OL,4,Cgovernment refusal of public inquiry
OL,6,FThe widow of GAA official Sean Brown
OL,7,Fhas secured High Court permission to
OL,8,Fchallenge the UK Government's failure
OL,9,Fto act on calls to establish a public
OL,10,Finquiry into his murder.
OL,12,FBridie Brown was granted leave to seek
OL,13,Fa judicial review against the
OL,14,FSecretary of State for not taking a
OL,15,Fdecision on the request made by a
OL,16,Fcoroner.
