OL,3,CSean Brown family to challenge
OL,4,Cgovernment refusal of public inquiry
OL,6,FMr Brown, 61, was abducted by a
OL,7,FLoyalist Volunteer Force (LVF) gang as
OL,8,Fhe locked the gates at Bellaghy Wolfe
OL,9,FTones GAA Club in Co Londonderry in
OL,10,FMay 1997.
OL,12,FThe father of six was bundled into the
OL,13,Fboot of his car, taken to Randalstown,
OL,14,FCo Antrim and shot dead.
OL,16,FIn March this year the coroner, Mr
OL,17,FJustice Kinney, declared that the
OL,18,Finquest could not continue because of
OL,19,Fmaterial being excluded or withheld on
OL,20,Fnational security grounds.
