OL,3,CSean Brown family to challenge
OL,4,Cgovernment refusal of public inquiry
OL,6,FBefore the hearing was halted,
OL,7,Fhowever, it emerged that state agents
OL,8,Fwere among more than 25 people linked
OL,9,Fby intelligence to the murder.
OL,11,FMr Justice Kinney wrote to Northern
OL,12,FIreland Secretary Chris Heaton-Harris,
OL,13,Fasking him to establish a public
OL,14,Finquiry and setting a four-week
OL,15,Fdeadline for taking a decision.
OL,17,FLawyers for Mrs Brown launched a legal
OL,18,Fchallenge over the failure to respond
OL,19,Fto that correspondence.
