OL,3,CSean Brown family to challenge
OL,4,Cgovernment refusal of public inquiry
OL,6,FThey alleged that it breached the
OL,7,Fstate's duty to provide an effective
OL,8,Finvestigation into her husband's death
OL,9,Funder Article 2 of the European
OL,10,FConvention on Human Rights.
OL,12,FA public inquiry is now the only
OL,13,Fviable way of meeting those
OL,14,Fobligations, according to their case.
OL,16,FIt was further contended that the
OL,17,FSecretary of State has acted
OL,18,Funlawfully amid public concern at the
OL,19,Fpotential involvement of agents in the
OL,20,Fmurder.
