OL,3,CSean Brown family to challenge
OL,4,Cgovernment refusal of public inquiry
OL,6,FWith Mrs Brown now aged 87 and having
OL,7,Ffought for decades to establish the
OL,8,Ffull circumstances surrounding her
OL,9,Fhusband's killing, the court was told
OL,10,Fthere is an urgency to the proceedings.
OL,12,FAt a review hearing today no-one
OL,13,Fappeared on behalf of the respondents.
OL,15,FHowever, Mr Justice Humphreys ruled
OL,16,Fthat Mrs Brown has established an
OL,17,Farguable case.
OL,19,FGranting leave for her to apply for a
OL,20,Fjudicial review, the judge listed the
OL,21,Fcase for full hearing later this month.
