OL,6,FOutside court the widow's solicitor,
OL,7,FNiall Murphy of KRW Law, said: "We are
OL,8,Fgrateful to the court for the
OL,9,Fexpeditious management of this
OL,10,Fimportant (challenge) and look forward
OL,11,Fto making our full application in open
OL,12,Fcourt."
OL,14,FIn a statement, the Brown family was
OL,15,Fcritical of the non-attendance by
OL,16,FGovernment representatives.
